  ('promotion-6ec17a12-moex-00038', 'promotion-6ec17a12', 'promotion-6ec17a12-moex-112-908552fe', 'sub-promotion-6ec17a12-02', NULL, 'essay', '偵查機關在偵辦特殊重大刑案時，通常會召集所需機關、成員共組專案小
