  ('promotion-6ec17a12-moex-00042', 'promotion-6ec17a12', 'promotion-6ec17a12-moex-112-3082b5f1', 'sub-promotion-6ec17a12-03', NULL, 'essay', '單行道、速限、禁鳴喇叭、禁止停車或禁止超車等交通標誌與標線之法
